                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Bangkok</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-10-20"><hi rend="italic">October 20,
